{"tid":1112330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(開始倒數)TVB今晚會刪走《開心速遞》主題曲","createTime":"2019-04-17T10:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T12:05:56.000Z","uid":199735,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1bae04fac9d9647c3bb2e5f5b8900f6b2ebc831a","tid":1112330,"uid":199735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"黃心穎許志安激吻事件形象插水 《開心速遞》主題曲被抽起<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bwwrNcr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbwwrNcr.jpg&h=02fe1a56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《開心速遞》在播出初期，起用曲調輕快的歌曲《latin soul strut》作為片頭音樂，自第225集起，改由黃心穎上陣，主唱歌主題曲《在心中》，但網上負評如潮，討論區連登更有一個長期帖文「不要黃心穎唱主題曲」。由於《開心速遞》是TVB皇牌劇集，又在合家歡時段播放，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不少網民揚言要罷聽主題曲，更甚者有人直言一聽到主題曲就想直接熄電視，如此群情洶湧</span></span>，據知情人士透露，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TVB馬上有所動作，今晚會刪掉主題曲</span></span>。今次心穎與許志安偷情，想不到連《開心速遞》都被牽連。<br />\n其實黃心穎不甘只做演員，做歌手才是她最大的目標。有指她為了完歌手夢，瘋狂去聽演唱會取經，又主動結交音樂人做朋友，有傳更因此而冷落男友馬國明。有指黃心穎前年專程過澳門看許志安演唱會，多次主動出擊而成功攻陷對方，成為裙下之臣。<br />\n作為一名準歌手，黃心穎可以主唱TVB最入屋劇集《開心速遞》主題曲，其實對她圓歌手夢甚有助力，今次偷情事件對她的演藝事業及歌唱前程打擊非常大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2jd52LW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2jd52LW.jpg&h=52806059&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/318698/%E9%BB%83%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E8%A8%B1%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%89%E6%BF%80%E5%90%BB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%8F%92%E6%B0%B4-%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E6%9B%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F318698%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%25A9%258E%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25BF%2580%25E5%2590%25BB%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BB%25B6%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E6%258F%2592%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25BF%2583%25E9%2580%259F%25E9%2581%259E-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%25A1%258C%25E6%259B%25B2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258A%25BD%25E8%25B5%25B7&d=BZ3h%2BuUaIL2OU9i9OZdAr8kuRvkIHaPazTq7BlmTy1I%3D&h=72a87013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/318698/%E9%BB%83%E5%BF%83%E7%A9%8E%E8%A8%B1%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%89%E6%BF%80%E5%90%BB%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E5%BD%A2%E8%B1%A1%E6%8F%92%E6%B0%B4-%E9%96%8B%E5%BF%83%E9%80%9F%E9%81%9E-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E6%9B%B2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8A%BD%E8%B5%B7</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">追撃非洲穎身敗名裂如同過街臭閪鼠！！！</span></span>終於成功踢走賓穎主題曲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就係你依啲仆街閪女人搞到係女人都俾人話臭雞，你死你事啦，累鳩啲女人，港女唔係個個都好似你咁臭閪格！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">TVB今晚刪就應記一功！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">正式倒數！！！！</span>"},{"pid":"a335167740ea90dae13698150d2c02d21b2e34ba","tid":1112330,"uid":115027,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:05:56.000Z","msg":"純音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}